.TH "ccw_device_get_mdc" 9 "ccw_device_get_mdc" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ccw_device_get_mdc \- accumulate max data count
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ccw_device_get_mdc
.BI "(struct ccw_device *cdev "  ","
.BI "u8 mask "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cdev" 12
ccw device for which the max data count is accumulated
.IP "mask" 12
mask of paths to use
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Return the number of 64K-bytes blocks all paths at least support
for a transport command. Return value 0 indicates failure.
